RELEASE NOTES for BANDIT
========================

This is the release "1.9.2" of the BANDIT toolkit.
This is a "STABLE" release.

See https://docs.phyglos.org/bandit for more information.


MAJOR CHANGES
=============

* Do not copy HOST build packs into the TARGET filesystem
* Add temporary users/groups 'bin' and 'tty' to the BUILDER system
* Removed unused BUILD_ variables
* Fixed error in bandit_find_catalog_MD5
* Show BUNDLE_SOURCES group when no origin can be found


